data.description: Step into contemporary elegance in this 2022-built home on 3.33 acres, offering sweeping farm land views. The open-concept design & 12'+ ceilings create a spacious, sunlit interior, accentuated by the gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, high-end appliances, pot-filler, walk-in pantry & a large breakfast nook. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace or unwind on the expansive covered patio.  4 bedrooms, each with a walk-in closet, provide ample space. The master suite boasts a vaulted ceiling, a lavish tile shower & a unique Walk-in Seasonal Master Closet. Work from home in your dedicated office & let your creativity flow in the unfinished upstairs area, perfect for a 5th bedroom, hobby room, game room, or man cave.  Embrace the charm of the covered front porch, ideal for savoring serene farm land vistas. This home seamlessly merges modern luxury with rural tranquility. Experience the beauty of country living without compromising on contemporary comforts. 1 year home warranty offered by Seller. Schedule your showing today & discover your dream home! Great Highway Access....& conveniently located near Restaurants, Schools & Shopping.
